sense.def:
To have dominance over a person, place, or group
pomeni imeti vpliv ali nadzor nad neko osebo, krajem ali skupino.

seg.quote: The treaty gave them dominance of the sea routes.

sense.def:
Tisto, kar ima
dominance
, velja za pomembnejše kot druge sorodne stvari.

seg.quote: ...the dominance of economics in social sciences.
